Notes: The library has approximately 20,000 fiction, nonfiction, large print and reference books.  Its collection also features DVD's, audio books, periodicals, 31 computers with Internet access, 6 laptops for in-house check-out, and the Alabama Virtual Library.  In addition, the library carries the following newspapers:  The Dothan Eagle, Daleville Sun-Courier, The Enterprise Ledger, Southern Star, Army Flier, The Sun, and The Wiregrass Aviator.
Source of Repository Data: Alabama Department of Archives and History
